!!!
How to play custom missions:

1) Join the game and find "Custom Mission" in the mission menu
2) Start a custom mission lobby
3) Go to the table and open the custom mission loader
4) Copy the URL of this page into the box and hit enter. It will NOT work if you copy the contents of this page instead of the URL.

Mission Name: The Transfer
Creator: @Sylvie09 (Disc) @s_Sylvie09 (Roblox)
Version: v1.0.1                       Wow look a random number why is that there -> 3
Briefing: A tome the Adversarialists are after is currently stuck in a government storage facility underground; you're going in to grab the tome before the cult can, as well as scrape information on artifacts and transfers from the building's servers. I hope your injuries from last mission weren't too bad - you're going to need your strength for this one.

!!!
